devdoc.details: Implements voting process along with vote delegation

delegate(address).details: Delegate your vote to the voter 'to'.

params.to: address to which vote is delegated

vote(bool).details: Give your vote (including votes delegated to you).

params.opinion_: index of opinion in the vote function

votingResult().details: Computes the winning proposal taking all previous votes into account.

returns._0: result index of winning proposal in the proposals array
